    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in museum-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and recently refreshed bushings to ensure factory-spec torsional rigidity. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry is perfectly preserved, utilizing OEM+ Bilstein dampers that maintain the factory's balanced damping profile while sharpening turn-in response. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero oxidation or clear-coat failure. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-tier example for the discerning purist.",
