      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, garage-kept, and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. You won\u2019t find a single blemish on this beauty\u2014it's truly been my 'baby.' I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate just how pristine this car is. Swing by, take a look, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
